                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18421128-39a-offence-1 t18421128-cd-34"></join>31st of Oct</rs>., 2 pairs of drawers, value 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 2 waistcoats, 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; 1 frock, 18<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; and 1 pair of trowsers, 18<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the goods of <persName id="t18421128-name-275" type="victimName">
