                        <interp inst="t18421128-name-279" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES MALIN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I took the prisoner at No. 9, Bluegate-place—I found this canvas frock and waistcoat lying on the floor by her side, and saw these two pain of flannel drawers and this other waistcoat found behind the door—the prisoner said she knew nothing at all about it.</p>
